    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台商家违规管理总则》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1301009720522588160",
    "content": "<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0in; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0in; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;您好，为适应业务发展需求，将修订《<a href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=2754\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">京东开放平台商家违规管理总则</a>》，现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年10月30日- 2025年11月5日，规则预计于 2025年11月6日生效，公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0in; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">&nbsp;修订内容如下：</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&ldquo;第七类不当经营&rdquo;中新增：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">30</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【恶意铺品】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1b1b1b; background: #F8F8F9;\">商家通过恶意使用批量发布工具、搬运他人商品、重复上架、信息造假等不当方式，上架大量无实质售卖价值、信息虚假、低质冗余的无效商品，导致店铺无效商品数量大幅激增、影响平台正常经营秩序的行为。 京东有权根据违规情节严重程度，对涉事商家店铺及关联店铺采取预警、开具违约单、管控、限权、关店等处理措施，包括但不限于：违规商品下架且限制重新上架、限制店铺内商品发布数量上限、限制每日新发商品数、全店商品流量降权 / 屏蔽、限制提报平台营销活动、限制关联品类商品上架、限制新品标识申请、限制 ISV 工具部分功能使用、限制商品信息批量编辑权限等。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1b1b1b; background: #F8F8F9;\">恶意铺品细则详见</span></strong><a href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1301009720522588160\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">关于新增《京东开放平台恶意铺品细则》的公示通知</a></p>\n<p class=\"summary\" style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: #8c8c8c; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-v-190b854e=\"\">&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"article-info\" style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-grow: 1; color: #000000; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-v-190b854e=\"\">\n<div class=\"meta-info\" style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-start; flex-direction: row; gap: 16px; color: #8c8c8c;\" data-v-190b854e=\"\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\">&nbsp;</p>",
